trans-unit.source: Visual Studio 2019 Highlights
trans-unit.target: Visual Studio 2019 Highlights

trans-unit.source: Whether you’re new to coding or ready for your next project, Visual Studio 2019 streamlines your experience so you can get right down to focused work.
trans-unit.target: Whether you’re new to coding or ready for your next project, Visual Studio 2019 streamlines your experience so you can get right down to focused work.

trans-unit.source: You'll find more screen space for your code and you can search for anything from one place.
trans-unit.target: You'll find more screen space for your code and you can search for anything from one place.

trans-unit.source: You can keep your code tidy with one-click code clean-up.
trans-unit.target: You can keep your code tidy with one-click code clean-up.

trans-unit.source: When you're debugging, you'll notice better stepping performance and you'll get search capabilities within the Autos, Locals, and Watch windows to quickly find that elusive object or value.

trans-unit.target: Visual Studio Preview gives you early access to the latest features and improvements not yet available in the main release.

trans-unit.source: Making every developer more productive with Visual Studio 2019

trans-unit.source: December 4th, 2018 by John Montgomery
trans-unit.target: December 4th, 2018 by John Montgomery

trans-unit.source: In Visual Studio 2019 Preview 1, we’ve focused on a few key areas, such as making it faster to open and work with projects stored in git repositories, improving IntelliSense with Artificial Intelligence (AI) (a feature we call Visual Studio IntelliCode), and making it easier to collaborate with your teammates by integrating Live Share.
trans-unit.target: In Visual Studio 2019 Preview 1, we’ve focused on a few key areas, such as making it faster to open and work with projects stored in git repositories, improving IntelliSense with Artificial Intelligence (AI) (a feature we call Visual Studio IntelliCode), and making it easier to collaborate with your teammates by integrating Live Share.

trans-unit.source: With each preview we’ll be adding capabilities, improving performance, and refining the user experience, and we absolutely want your feedback.
trans-unit.target: With each preview we’ll be adding capabilities, improving performance, and refining the user experience, and we absolutely want your feedback.
